  "label": "Jorren Halvik",
  "description": "A broad-shouldered man of middle years, built with the compact strength of habitual manual work and long hours on his feet. Brown eyes sit beneath heavy lids, giving his gaze a steady, appraising cast that rarely softens. Black hair is worn in a shortknot, kept practical and close against heat and grime. Bronze skin shows ingrained weathering at the knuckles and along the forearms, consistent with frequent washing and repeated contact with harsh cleansers.",
